data.description: Welcome home to this 3 Bed/2 FULL Bath historic charmer featuring original hardwoods, tons of natural light, updated kitchen and bathrooms. From the covered front porch to the welcoming tall ceilings, neutral paint, and fireplace insert, the living room is the perfect spot to entertain or relax.  Kitchen boats stainless steel refrigerator and gas stove with farmhouse sink and updated faucet. Beautiful staircase leads you upstairs to a bedroom and master suite where you can relax in the claw tub.  Master bedroom has extra storage space or easily convert this space to your own walk-in closet.  The backyard is the perfect oasis with mature trees and fully fenced privacy fence. Windows and HVAC are newer.  Roof is less than 10 years old.
